			<tr>
			<td>
				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    Karg Icebear</b>&nbsp;<a href="../Subscribe.asp?DID=7608"><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
					<b><a href="mailto:">Anonymous</a> | 
		                        1/9/2000 3:51:29 AM</b></font></p>
					
					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">In Everfrost, theres an NPC named Karg Icebear that wanders around the first part of the plains of Everfrost (The part before the river). I you talk to him you'll find out he can make some pretty nifty items. One of these items is the Polar Bear Cloak. Another thing he can make has something to do with werewolf paws. Any info related to this would be appreciated. Also if you kill him, he gives an even BETTER cloak. It's called the Cloak of the Ice Bear.
			<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
					</p>
			</td>
			</tr>
