<BR>
<BR>
He is a random random random random spawn. With the gaunts I waited 6 hours one day and 4 another to get him then a few hours later he showed up again (I was hunting in permafrost). I'm on the cloak quest now and it's been 8 straight hours of no spawn, or at least not to my knowlege.<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
The werewolf items are super, but finding Karg is a pain<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Werewolves are most commonly camped by sitting in the middle of the road in the canyon near quenos hills and watching TV until he runs up and whacks you for a pre-emptive double 45.<BR>
<BR>
